{"tid":1496529,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［幫手推］巴打絲打Facebook Club 2位Admin 被恐嚇要收聲，否則會採取進一步行動！","createTime":"2019-08-22T14:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T15:54:51.000Z","uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a58c49672c2627ab37c433e9c68f71b918c7335","tid":1496529,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:36:49.000Z","msg":"我和Coco被恐嚇，叫我地收聲。<br />\n否則會採取進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n剛才我哋吃緊飯，手機WhatsApp突然不斷收到同一則內容的WhatsApp。內容大致要我地收口不要再亂說話。<br />\n<br />\n佢地由8:59至9:30，大約用100個不同的電話號碼，send左一模一樣的訊息黎，期間完全冇撞過機，十足0.5/打手用電腦洗版的手法。<br />\n<br />\n其實今次都不是我和Coco 第一次收到恐嚇訊息，記得大約半年前（巴打絲打群組出事前），我們事前都有收到這類型訊息，但當時我們沒有理會。<br />\n<br />\n結果，巴打絲打群組被封鎖，我和Coco 被大量打手account攻擊，他們不斷改圖、以假證據抹黑我地。同時，他們有很多分身戶口躲藏在香港各個Facebook群組中，假戶口不斷發佈所謂的證據，一唱一和，假都變成真！<br />\n他們給我的罪名有很多，又說我們是澳門人，又說我們是打手抹黑其他公司，又說我們收了許多黑錢，又說我們經營賭檔，甚至說Coco假學歷、變性、整容等等&hellip;&hellip; &hellip;&hellip;簡直無稽，我都廢事回應！<br />\n<br />\n幸好各位巴打絲打還相信我們，留在我們的群組，今次我把這些WhatsApp對話放出來，是避免再重複上一次的情況和誤會。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我不是一個喜歡畫公仔畫出腸的人，但今次無奈真的要向大家報備一聲，就算他日我和Coco又出事 或群組死了，大家都知道原因。<br />\n<br />\n巴打絲打 Facebook Club （巴打絲打 Facebook Club) 就只有這一個，其他的都不是我管理的。他們不懷好意，希望大家不要加入他們。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我想問下，我應該點做？<br />\nLink:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1767225003619858/?sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F295202647488775%2Fpermalink%2F1767225003619858%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LaT%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=5baff3b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1767225003619858/?sfnsn=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idNwTkD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidNwTkD.png&h=09b7aaa5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MtSMHeo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtSMHeo.png&h=6046c0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pd0a8UK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpd0a8UK.png&h=be63d8f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdf8578646af695ac8e04f3943cade9a6ad69a37","tid":1496529,"uid":251836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e461586dcfbfd449e3c4da36181ed4370f8a45","tid":1496529,"uid":182827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6e35781d3368f118c1456d50406651ee7deb37","tid":1496529,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:40:55.000Z","msg":"呢件事好大劑！第一個被滅聲嘅Facebook page！<br />\n之後會有更多個！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913b6dd56e13dee5665aefd44c6d6bdf456a2db5","tid":1496529,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S3F2Z3p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS3F2Z3p.png&h=737848aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eeec55d958c8e7d55ae281c4facde4e9787e70b3","tid":1496529,"uid":241567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:54:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}